Dialogue: 0.0:30:25.45.0:30:30.55.Dialogue3.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(178.394)\i1}You get to be more you than you have{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:30:25.45.0:30:30.55.Dialogue3.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(241.421)\i1}been in a very long time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:30:30.79.0:30:33.26.Dialogue3.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(199.421)\i1}You deserve everything you want.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:30:33.76.0:30:35.35.Dialogue3.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(243.394)\i1}I have a hotel{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:30:33.76.0:30:35.35.Dialogue3.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(292.420)\i1}in Park Place.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:30:35.60.0:30:40.16.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(203.420)}which brings your total to $1.500.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:40.43.0:30:41.90.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(206.421)}Sorry. Bee. It's nothing personal.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:42.17.0:30:44.40.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(214.421)}Yeah. I know. It's just business.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:44.64.0:30:46.04.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(305.419)}Mmm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:48.81.0:30:50.33.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(280.421)}Ew. It's my mom.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:50.58.0:30:51.70.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(271.419)}Should I answer it?
Dialogue: 0.0:30:51.91.0:30:53.14.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(325.421)}No!
Dialogue: 0.0:30:53.41.0:30:55.38.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(250.392)}What if it's about Chic?
Dialogue: 0.0:30:53.41.0:30:55.38.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(301.421)}Let me just...
Dialogue: 0.0:30:56.72.0:30:58.24.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(257.421)}Hey. Mom. what's up?
Dialogue: 0.0:30:58.49.0:31:02.39.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(221.394)}By the way. when are we ever
Dialogue: 0.0:30:58.49.0:31:02.39.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(244.421)}gonna get to meet Chic?
Dialogue: 0.0:31:02.62.0:31:04.22.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(232.421)}I actually did before we left.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:04.66.0:31:06.56.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(287.419)}And how is he?
Dialogue: 0.0:31:08.36.0:31:10.52.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(231.421)}Honestly. he's kinda creepy.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:10.76.0:31:12.89.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(286.394)\i1}Guys...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:31:10.76.0:31:12.89.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(274.421)}- Everything okay?
Dialogue: 0.0:31:13.13.0:31:14.69.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(304.421)}No. actually.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:15.60.0:31:18.00.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(206.421)}My mom is freaking out because
Dialogue: 0.0:31:18.77.0:31:21.47.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(228.394)}Hiram Lodge just bought the
Dialogue: 0.0:31:18.77.0:31:21.47.Dialogue3.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(267.421)\i1}Riverdale Register.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:31:31.35.0:31:32.94.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(231.421)}My mom is losing her mind.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:33.19.0:31:34.78.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(205.421)}My dad's not answering her calls.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:35.02.0:31:37.12.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(182.394)}Veronica. did you know your dad was
Dialogue: 0.0:31:35.02.0:31:37.12.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(261.421)}buying the {\i1}Register?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:31:37.36.0:31:39.29.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(209.421)}What? No. Betty. of course not.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:39.53.0:31:40.76.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(200.421)}See. this is what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:40.99.0:31:41.83.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(286.421)}Relax. Jughead.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:42.13.0:31:44.16.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(253.392)}- Don't tell me to relax--
Dialogue: 0.0:31:42.13.0:31:44.16.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(188.421)}- Is that why you brought us up here?
Dialogue: 0.0:31:44.40.0:31:44.99.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(340.419)}Yes.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:45.20.0:31:46.89.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(189.394)}To get us out of town while your dad
Dialogue: 0.0:31:45.20.0:31:46.89.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(246.421)}was doing these things?
Dialogue: 0.0:31:47.13.0:31:49.16.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(217.421)}Okay. now who sounds crazy?
Dialogue: 0.0:31:49.40.0:31:52.46.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(202.394)}Lodge Industries has been buying
Dialogue: 0.0:31:49.40.0:31:52.46.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(204.421)}properties all over the Southside.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:52.71.0:31:54.97.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(167.421)}Now he buys the one newspaper in town.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:55.21.0:31:56.80.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(242.394)}so people can't report on
Dialogue: 0.0:31:55.21.0:31:56.80.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(281.421)}what he's doing?
Dialogue: 0.0:31:57.01.0:31:58.98.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(256.394)}It's a classic gambit of
Dialogue: 0.0:31:57.01.0:31:58.98.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(248.419)}mobsters and criminals.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:59.21.0:32:00.41.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(240.421)}Shut the hell up. Jughead.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:00.65.0:32:02.81.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(197.394)}Archie. this one's pretty simple. so
Dialogue: 0.0:32:00.65.0:32:02.81.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(201.421)}even you might be able to get this
Dialogue: 0.0:32:03.05.0:32:05.64.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(198.394)}if you stopped kissing up to Hiram
Dialogue: 0.0:32:03.05.0:32:05.64.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(256.420)}for. like. two seconds.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:05.89.0:32:07.48.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(176.421)}How many times have I defended you?
Dialogue: 0.0:32:07.75.0:32:10.31.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(216.394)}And now you turn and stab my
Dialogue: 0.0:32:07.75.0:32:10.31.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(272.421)}family in the back?
Dialogue: 0.0:32:10.59.0:32:11.85.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(176.421)}It sounds to me like you should be mad
Dialogue: 0.0:32:12.16.0:32:14.69.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(183.394)}at your dad for selling the newspaper.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:12.16.0:32:14.69.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(317.419)}not mine.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:14.93.0:32:17.99.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(218.394)}Yeah. there's nothing. like. evil
Dialogue: 0.0:32:14.93.0:32:17.99.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(234.421)}about buying a newspaper.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:18.23.0:32:19.89.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(191.394)}He's trying to silence the free press.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:18.23.0:32:19.89.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(327.419)}Archie.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:20.13.0:32:21.97.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(209.394)}He's trying to keep Mrs. Cooper
Dialogue: 0.0:32:20.13.0:32:21.97.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(252.421)}from coming after him.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:22.24.0:32:24.80.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(268.394)}I am so sick of your
Dialogue: 0.0:32:22.24.0:32:24.80.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(240.421)}vendetta against my dad.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:25.04.0:32:26.10.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(208.421)}He's done plenty of good things.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:26.31.0:32:29.14.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(213.421)}Oh. like what? Name one thing.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:29.51.0:32:30.17.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(332.419)}He's...
Dialogue: 0.0:32:30.38.0:32:31.94.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(215.421)}He paid my dad's medical bills.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:32.18.0:32:34.84.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(213.394)}Boy. Archie. Veronica's got you
Dialogue: 0.0:32:32.18.0:32:34.84.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(211.421)}wrapped around her little finger.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:35.08.0:32:36.45.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(227.421)}And other parts of her body.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:36.68.0:32:38.98.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(298.421)}Oh! I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:39.42.0:32:41.35.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(228.394)}I'm sorry we don't spend our
Dialogue: 0.0:32:39.42.0:32:41.35.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(281.421)}time being tragic
Dialogue: 0.0:32:41.59.0:32:44.72.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(190.394)}and moping and holding hands while
Dialogue: 0.0:32:41.59.0:32:44.72.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(190.421)}watching serial killer documentaries.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:44.96.0:32:48.26.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(178.394)}Oh. and wearing costumes to role-play
Dialogue: 0.0:32:44.96.0:32:48.26.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(266.421)}to get our rocks off.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:50.96.0:32:52.36.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(226.392)}- Where did that come from?
Dialogue: 0.0:32:50.96.0:32:52.36.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(221.419)}- Who else knows we're here?
Dialogue: 0.0:32:52.60.0:32:53.79.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(237.421)}Why'd you say it like that?
Dialogue: 0.0:32:54.03.0:32:55.09.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(295.421)}- Oh. my God.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:55.30.0:32:56.77.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(197.419)}You rich summer folks never learn.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:56.97.0:32:58.67.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(195.421)}You just keep walking around town.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:58.94.0:33:00.97.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(247.394)}flashing more cash than
Dialogue: 0.0:32:58.94.0:33:00.97.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(280.421)}we see in a year.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:01.21.0:33:02.34.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(207.421)}We're gonna take what we want.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:02.58.0:33:03.54.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(242.421)}and then we're gonna go.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:04.08.0:33:05.20.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(214.421)}If you guys behave yourselves.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:05.41.0:33:07.51.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(193.421)}nobody gets their skulls knocked in.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:09.92.0:33:11.65.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(242.421)}Fine. take what you want.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:11.85.0:33:13.01.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(214.421)}We won't give you any trouble.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:13.25.0:33:14.35.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(262.421)}Where's your purse?
Dialogue: 0.0:33:15.09.0:33:16.52.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(317.420)}Um. it's...
Dialogue: 0.0:33:18.09.0:33:19.42.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(287.421)}In my bedroom.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:19.79.0:33:21.56.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(239.394)}- Let's go to the bedroom.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:19.79.0:33:21.56.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(298.421)\i1}No.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:33:21.80.0:33:24.23.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(203.394)}No way are you going with her up
Dialogue: 0.0:33:21.80.0:33:24.23.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(274.421)}there alone. I'll go.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:24.46.0:33:27.40.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(287.420)}Archie. it's fine.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:27.63.0:33:29.19.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(315.419)}I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:29.44.0:33:30.77.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(271.421)}We'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:31.00.0:33:33.06.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(195.421)}Everybody just needs to stay calm.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:43.65.0:33:45.14.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(294.419)}It's over there.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:45.85.0:33:48.29.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(207.421)}I'm just going to pick it up. okay?
Dialogue: 0.0:33:59.13.0:34:00.62.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(245.421)}Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0.0:34:09.01.0:34:10.81.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(209.421)}You think I don't recognize you?
Dialogue: 0.0:34:11.31.0:34:12.11.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(286.419)}From the store?
Dialogue: 0.0:34:12.35.0:34:13.64.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(230.421)}Shut up and get your wallet.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:37.97.0:34:38.77.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(266.421)}Can we go already?
Dialogue: 0.0:34:39.04.0:34:39.84.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(275.421)}You got the cash?
Dialogue: 0.0:34:40.07.0:34:41.77.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(263.421)}Yeah. I got the cash.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:42.01.0:34:43.31.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(213.421)}Then you got what you wanted.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:43.54.0:34:46.57.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(251.421)}Not everything. not yet.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:46.81.0:34:48.81.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(261.394)}Why don't you all get
Dialogue: 0.0:34:46.81.0:34:48.81.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(260.421)}down on your knees?
Dialogue: 0.0:34:49.08.0:34:50.64.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(210.420)}Come on. man. let's not do this.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:50.88.0:34:51.58.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(322.421)}Shut up.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:51.82.0:34:54.15.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(260.421)}I said. on your knees.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:54.39.0:34:56.19.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(239.421)}Hands behind your backs.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:56.42.0:34:57.62.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(295.421)}Do it!
Dialogue: 0.0:35:12.17.0:35:13.66.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(286.419)}It's a nice cabin.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:14.37.0:35:16.61.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(237.394)}I'm sorry we have to make
Dialogue: 0.0:35:14.37.0:35:16.61.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(279.419)}such a mess in it.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:19.21.0:35:20.65.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(287.419)}The hell is that?
Dialogue: 0.0:35:20.88.0:35:22.71.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(190.421)}That would be the security company
Dialogue: 0.0:35:22.95.0:35:25.48.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(199.394)}calling to check on the silent alarm
Dialogue: 0.0:35:22.95.0:35:25.48.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(267.421)}I hit in my bedroom.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:25.75.0:35:27.85.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(198.394)}I'd say you hillbillies have about 30
Dialogue: 0.0:35:25.75.0:35:27.85.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(266.419)}seconds to run for it
Dialogue: 0.0:35:28.09.0:35:29.68.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(271.394)}before this place is
Dialogue: 0.0:35:28.09.0:35:29.68.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(259.421)}swarming with guards
Dialogue: 0.0:35:29.92.0:35:32.15.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(233.392)}who will shoot first and ask
Dialogue: 0.0:35:29.92.0:35:32.15.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(283.421)}questions never.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:36.90.0:35:38.56.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(259.421)}Screw you. rich bitch.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:41.47.0:35:43.44.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(243.394)}Archie. don't!
Dialogue: 0.0:35:41.47.0:35:43.44.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(262.421)}No. Arch!
Dialogue: 0.0:36:00.92.0:36:02.65.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(288.421)}Andre...
Dialogue: 0.0:36:02.89.0:36:04.38.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(180.394)}There were some other guys with him.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:02.89.0:36:04.38.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(272.421)}Did you see them?
Dialogue: 0.0:36:04.62.0:36:07.53.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(247.392)}Go back to the cabin. I'll
Dialogue: 0.0:36:04.62.0:36:07.53.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(279.419)}take it from here.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:08.60.0:36:09.36.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(242.421)}What are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0.0:36:09.60.0:36:10.56.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(333.420)}I said.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:11.33.0:36:12.70.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(282.419)}I'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:44.36.0:36:48.30.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(233.394)}First of all. thank you. Mom
Dialogue: 0.0:36:44.36.0:36:48.30.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(279.419)}and Sheriff Keller
Dialogue: 0.0:36:48.54.0:36:50.60.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(198.421)}for coming to meet me and Kevin.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:50.87.0:36:52.81.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(207.421)}We promise you this isn't a trap.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:53.04.0:36:56.57.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(246.392)}It's that Kevin and I were
Dialogue: 0.0:36:53.04.0:36:56.57.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(252.421)}talking after the movie.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:56.81.0:36:58.80.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(280.421)}and we thought...
Dialogue: 0.0:36:59.11.0:37:01.88.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(232.394)}This conversation is bigger
Dialogue: 0.0:36:59.11.0:37:01.88.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(263.421)}than just two people.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:02.08.0:37:04.61.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(229.394)}It's bigger than the people in
Dialogue: 0.0:37:02.08.0:37:04.61.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(281.420)}this booth. even.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:04.85.0:37:07.55.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(177.421)}And it's probably gonna be a long one.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:07.79.0:37:11.45.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(242.421)}so we should get started.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:22.00.0:37:24.56.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(190.394)}Now you may think you've mastered
Dialogue: 0.0:37:22.00.0:37:24.56.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(260.420)}the art of silent tears.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:24.80.0:37:27.30.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(235.394)}but I saw you crying during
Dialogue: 0.0:37:24.80.0:37:27.30.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(271.421)}that movie. Cheryl.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:27.57.0:37:29.07.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(259.421)}I never cry at movies.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:29.31.0:37:31.34.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(245.421)}Real life's tragic enough.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:32.35.0:37:34.58.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(250.419)}But when Simon's mom
Dialogue: 0.0:37:34.81.0:37:37.94.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(239.392)}said he used to be such a
Dialogue: 0.0:37:34.81.0:37:37.94.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(244.421)}carefree kid. growing up.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:38.18.0:37:40.38.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(238.421)}and then at a certain point
Dialogue: 0.0:37:40.59.0:37:43.96.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(210.421)}he stopped being that happy kid
Dialogue: 0.0:37:44.22.0:37:46.09.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(209.394)}because he was hiding a secret.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:44.22.0:37:46.09.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(328.421)}it just...
Dialogue: 0.0:37:46.43.0:37:47.79.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(322.421)}Cheryl...
Dialogue: 0.0:37:49.20.0:37:52.53.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(250.394)}Everyone thinks I'm this
Dialogue: 0.0:37:49.20.0:37:52.53.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(278.420)}loveless monster.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:53.73.0:37:55.20.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(293.419)}but it isn't true.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:57.60.0:37:59.87.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(249.421)}I loved someone
Dialogue: 0.0:38:00.57.0:38:02.20.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(291.419)}who loved me.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:03.91.0:38:06.00.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(225.421)}And my mother destroyed it.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:06.25.0:38:08.04.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(214.421)}You mean your brother Jason?
Dialogue: 0.0:38:09.68.0:38:11.71.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(203.421)}I heard how close you guys were.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:12.15.0:38:14.82.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(284.421)}No. not Jay-Jay.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:17.39.0:38:20.49.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(250.419)}Her name was Heather.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:25.20.0:38:28.07.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(184.421)}She was my best friend in junior high.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:28.64.0:38:31.07.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(173.421)}She used to sleep over every weekend.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:31.57.0:38:33.54.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(258.421)}Until one night.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:33.77.0:38:36.47.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(180.421)}my mother caught us in the same bed.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:36.68.0:38:39.98.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(243.419)}She said I was "deviant".
Dialogue: 0.0:38:41.08.0:38:43.21.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(259.421)}Cheryl. I am so sorry.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:44.08.0:38:46.55.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(236.394)}But you have to know your
Dialogue: 0.0:38:44.08.0:38:46.55.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(285.421)}mother's wrong.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:47.29.0:38:49.15.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(268.419)}You're not loveless.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:49.39.0:38:52.19.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(238.421)}You're not deviant. Okay?
Dialogue: 0.0:38:54.23.0:38:57.22.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(271.419)}You're sensational.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:06.64.0:39:09.40.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(221.392)}Thank God Andre didn't leave
Dialogue: 0.0:39:06.64.0:39:09.40.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(274.419)}when I told him to.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:11.91.0:39:14.68.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(184.394)}Thank God you didn't catch up to that
Dialogue: 0.0:39:11.91.0:39:14.68.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(265.421)}hillbilly in the woods.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:14.91.0:39:16.64.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(220.421)}He might've killed you. Archie.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:16.92.0:39:18.48.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(244.419)}and that would've been...
Dialogue: 0.0:39:32.87.0:39:33.66.Dialogue3.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(182.421)\i1}Archie didn't say any more{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:39:33.93.0:39:36.20.Dialogue3.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(192.394)\i1}about what happened in the woods{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:39:33.93.0:39:36.20.Dialogue3.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(277.421)\i1}that terrible night.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:39:36.87.0:39:39.03.Dialogue3.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(271.420)\i1}At least. not to us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:39:42.88.0:39:44.90.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(254.392)}Veronica told me what
Dialogue: 0.0:39:42.88.0:39:44.90.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(254.421)}happened in the cabin.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:46.31.0:39:48.21.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(230.419)}And Andre told me the rest.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:48.45.0:39:49.92.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(244.394)}You did the right thing by
Dialogue: 0.0:39:48.45.0:39:49.92.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(277.421)}telling those boys
Dialogue: 0.0:39:50.15.0:39:51.55.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(183.421)}to take what they wanted and get out.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:51.75.0:39:53.31.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(249.419)}It was the smart choice.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:54.82.0:39:56.15.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(257.421)}It was the only choice.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:58.56.0:40:00.72.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(183.421)}Thank you for saying that. Mr. Lodge.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:06.50.0:40:08.26.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(242.421)}What happened between
Dialogue: 0.0:40:09.07.0:40:10.97.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(232.419)}Andre and that miscreant...
Dialogue: 0.0:40:12.71.0:40:14.14.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(265.421)}Did that bother you?
Dialogue: 0.0:40:15.58.0:40:18.55.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(281.419)}What Andre did?
Dialogue: 0.0:40:21.85.0:40:23.98.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(179.421)}The night we stopped the Black Hood.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:26.15.0:40:28.35.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(199.421)}there's only one thing that I regret.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:29.56.0:40:31.02.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(316.419)}I had him.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:31.52.0:40:34.15.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(204.394)}The man who tried to kill my dad.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:31.52.0:40:34.15.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(316.419)}I had him.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:35.90.0:40:36.99.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(286.419)}And I hesitated.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:38.90.0:40:39.92.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(223.421)}And he might've gotten away
Dialogue: 0.0:40:40.17.0:40:41.73.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(230.419)}if it wasn't for Sheriff Keller.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:42.24.0:40:45.21.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(226.394)}When it comes to protecting
Dialogue: 0.0:40:42.24.0:40:45.21.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(227.421)}yourself or your loved ones.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:47.01.0:40:49.34.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(241.421)}you never. ever. hesitate.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:03.76.0:41:07.25.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(180.421)}You can stop worrying now. I'm home.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:08.13.0:41:09.72.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(245.394)}As we were driving back
Dialogue: 0.0:41:08.13.0:41:09.72.Dialogue3.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(272.421)}from {\i1}The Shining.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:41:09.96.0:41:11.30.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(290.421)}I was thinking...
Dialogue: 0.0:41:11.53.0:41:13.59.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(232.392)}There's more than one kind
Dialogue: 0.0:41:11.53.0:41:13.59.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(276.419)}of home invasion.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:13.83.0:41:15.80.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(217.421)}It's not always fast and violent.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:16.07.0:41:17.16.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(220.421)}Sometimes we open the door
Dialogue: 0.0:41:17.40.0:41:19.30.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(189.419)}and we let the intruders in ourselves.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:20.27.0:41:21.64.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(264.421)}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0.0:41:23.48.0:41:26.47.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(198.394)}Before we left. I got a
Dialogue: 0.0:41:23.48.0:41:26.47.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(232.421)}really weird vibe from Chic.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:28.41.0:41:30.18.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(257.421)}Just be careful. okay?
Dialogue: 0.0:41:36.66.0:41:38.02.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(335.394)}- Bye.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:36.66.0:41:38.02.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(335.421)}- Bye.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:43.80.0:41:46.16.Dialogue3.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(217.394)\i1}And so this chapter{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:41:43.80.0:41:46.16.Dialogue3.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(278.419)\i1}comes full circle.{\i0}
